description:
Bob Burnquist N.ew F.ronT.ier Collectible Trading Cards
Limited Edition Series

Year 1991 (30 Years Pro Celebration)
A ride through my history with collectible Crypto Trading Cards using the Burnquist Gold Certificate of Authenticity. 

The time was special and this photo was taken by my friend Toninho,  he was a great friend and a stylish Vert skater. We were doing couch tricks for fun so I asked him to take a photo with my 35mm snapshot camera. Toninho has since passed away but the memory he snapped stayed. I turned pro that year and have been having fun ever since.
